commit_message:
fix the XML/JSON inconsistence in api cloudpipe:create

change the json response of cloudpipe:create {'instance_id': xxxxxx}

to {'cloudpipe': {'instance_id': xxxxxx}}

Partially implements bp: v3-api-inconsistencies

